events.text: hey, ninth me! how ya doing?
well, you’re here, so you must not be doing that well, but it could definitely be worse.
you’re not looking for our fourth death story, are you? geez! not my responsibility to shell out my life story. you’re me, you should already know, anyway!
quit staring. i’m not going to tell you.
if we’d kept our mouth shut back then, maybe it wouldn’t have ended so soon. i’ve learned my lesson.
